data.description: Great home in fantastic condition. Home has had some updating recently with paint and flooring. 4 bedrooms, 2 baths on a large fenced lot. Finished sq ft is 1651 and total is 2000. Two car garage and RV parking too. Home features hardwood floors, tile, and new carpet. Primary bedroom is huge with its own bath. Gas furnace (inspected every year) and hot water tank. Walking distance to school, shopping and more. Bus line is nearby too.
